beware the detours, the pitfalls, the traps. Cunningly positioned are
those cleverly disguised maka-fekes [octopus lures] beckoning us to grasp
them and to lose that which we most desire. Do not be deceived. Pause
to pray. Listen to that still, small voice which speaks to the depths
of our souls the Master's gentle invitation, 'Come, follow me' (Luke
